# Placeholder for qwen15b-lora-v0.1 adapter

This directory will contain the trained LoRA adapter after running:
  
  python training/qwen15b_lora/train.py

Expected files:
- adapter_config.json
- adapter_model.bin or adapter_model.safetensors
- metadata.json
- checksums.sha256
- tokenizer files

Adapter size: <400 MB target

